  - {* /ai-code-exercises/use-cases/code-algorithms/javascript/TaskManager/models.js}[models.js] specifically the `TaskStatus` enum line object, and the `Task` class by adding a new method `isAbandoned`.
  - {* /ai-code-exercises/use-cases/code-algorithms/javascript/TaskManager/storage.js}[storage.js],  the `TaskStorage` class by adding a new method to get `abandoned` tasks. `TaskStorage's load method` would only need to be modidied
    because when we load the tasks from storage and about to set the `status`, we can perform the check of whether its abandoned task or not.

